<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٥٩٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6952">يَحْيَى بْنُ بُكَيْرٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5348">اللَّيْثُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7248">يُونُسَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">ابْنِ شِهَابٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2436">سَعِيدِ بْنِ الْمُسَيَّبِ: </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبَا هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«يُخَرِّبُ الْكَعْبَةَ ذُو السُّوَيْقَتَيْنِ مِنَ الْحَبَشَةِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>